text:
America's First Reality Family turned out for Kourtney Kardashian's 39th birthday party, including Kim Kardashian and Kanye West—who spent the event being super adorable and at one point making out. KIDS MOMS AND DADS THESE DAYS!



Kim posted her ~passionate moment~ with Kanye to Instagram Stories, asking him "Babe, do you want to go to Dave Chappelle or do you want to go to the studio?" before sitting on his lap for some lip-to-lip action.
